IRCbot is program for find defined keys in IRC channel and
send msgs with these keys to SYSLOG server.

Compile:
    $ make

Run:
    $ ./ircbot <host>[:<port>] <channel> <syslog_server> [list]

<host> IRC server hostname
[<[port>] IRC server port (optional)
"<channel>" IRC channel to join conversation
<syslog_server> SYSLOG server to send logs
"[list]" list of keys

Example:
    $ ./ircbot irc.freenode.net] #ISA2014 192.168.1.12 "ISA,test,IRC"

List of files:
    Makefile
    main.cpp
    main.h
    README
